Yes, I killed people in a game....so? I never said I wasn't violent and didn't need help. Either way, I'm not the one whose whole taste in games relies on violence.Maybe its just me. Maybe I'm among the last generation of true gamers, the ones who played the game <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>to play the game</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and not care if I get to see blood or not. However, I can't see people saying Harris and Klebold didn't need help.<br>
