What do sales have to do with anything? Did I say that all gamers don't like violent games? No. <br>
I simply said that if one finds a game boring because they didn't get to kill people, then I'd hate to see those people when they grow up..... Correction: I'd like to see those people <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>grow up.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
